'''Safidine Industries''' was an elite weapons producer that had a contract to produce specialty [[Blaster/Legends|blasters]] for the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]]. The company had to put out a [[Bounty/Legends|bounty]] on [[Devidia Vennsiol]] after she and her boyfriend [[Dorbus Kyrullus]] had stolen secret prototypes.

